    function MakeDraggable(p9)
        local u10 = nil
        local u11 = nil
        local u12 = nil
        local u13 = nil

        local function u16(p14)
            local v15 = p14.Position - u13

            p9.Position = UDim2.new(u10.X.Scale, u10.X.Offset + v15.X, u10.Y.Scale, u10.Y.Offset + v15.Y)
        end

        p9.InputBegan:Connect(function(p17)
            if p17.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 or p17.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
                u11 = true
                u13 = p17.Position
                u10 = p9.Position

                p17.Changed:Connect(function()
                    if p17.UserInputState == Enum.UserInputState.End then
                        u11 = false
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)
        p9.InputChanged:Connect(function(p18)
            if p18.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement or p18.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.Touch then
                u12 = p18
            end
        end)
        _UserInputService.InputChanged:Connect(function(p19)
            if p19 == u12 and u11 then
                u16(p19)
            end
        end)
    end

    local function u42()

        local v35 = _t.hour % 24
        local v36 = v35 < 12 and 'AM' or 'PM'
        local __02i02i02is = string.format('%02i:%02i:%02i %s', (v35 - 1) % 12 + 1, _t.min, _t.sec, v36)
        local __02d02d04d = string.format('%02d/%02d/%04d', _t.day, _t.month, _t.year)
        local _LocalizationService = game:GetService('LocalizationService')
        local _LocalPlayer = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer
        local _ = _LocalPlayer.Name
        local _, v41 = pcall(function()
            return _LocalizationService:GetCountryRegionForPlayerAsync(_LocalPlayer)
        end)

        u20:Set(__02d02d04d .. ' - ' .. __02i02i02is .. ' [ ' .. v41 .. ' ]')
    end

spawn(function()
    pcall(function()
        if u6:ValidateKey('keyless') then
            LoadScript()
        else
            local _THUNDERZKeytxt = isfile('THUNDERZKey.txt')

            if _THUNDERZKeytxt and _THUNDERZKeytxt ~= nil then
                print('File ditemukan, mencoba membaca key...')

                local v69, v70 = pcall(function()
                    return readfile('THUNDERZKey.txt')
                end)

                if v69 and (v70 ~= nil and v70 ~= '') then
                    print('Found The Key: ' .. v70)

                    if u6:ValidateKey(v70) then
                        print('Success')
                        u5({
                            Title = 'Key System',
                            Content = 'Found Existing Key! Load Script',
                            Delay = 2,
                        })
                        LoadScript()
                    else
                        print('Key Expired')
                        u5({
                            Title = 'Key System',
                            Content = 'Expired Key.',
                            Delay = 3,
                        })
                        KeySystem()
                    end
                else
                    print('Gagal membaca file atau file kosong.')
                    KeySystem()
                end
            else
                print('File tidak ditemukan.')
                KeySystem()
            end
        end
    end)
end)

function LoadSettings()
    if readfile and (writefile and (isfile and isfolder)) then
        if not isfolder('ThunderZ Hub') then
            makefolder('ThunderZ Hub')
        end
        if not isfolder('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits') then
            makefolder('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits')
        end
        if isfile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json') then
            local v71 = game:GetService('HttpService'):JSONDecode(readfile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json'))
            local v72, v73, v74 = pairs(v71)

            while true do
                local v75

                v74, v75 = v72(v73, v74)

                if v74 == nil then
                    break
                end

                _G.Settings[v74] = v75
            end
        else
            writefile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json', game:GetService('HttpService'):JSONEncode(_G.Settings))
        end
    else
        local _ = warn
    end
end
function SaveSettings()
    if readfile and (writefile and (isfile and isfolder)) then
        if isfile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json') then
            game:GetService('HttpService'):JSONDecode(readfile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json'))

            local v76, v77, v78 = pairs(_G.Settings)
            local v79 = {}

            while true do
                local v80

                v78, v80 = v76(v77, v78)

                if v78 == nil then
                    break
                end

                v79[v78] = v80
            end

            writefile('ThunderZ Hub/Blox Fruits/' .. game.Players.LocalPlayer.Name .. '.json', game:GetService('HttpService'):JSONEncode(v79))
        else
            LoadSettings()
        end
    else
        local _ = warn
    end
end

        function BTP(p116)
            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.Head:Destroy()

            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = p116

            wait(1)

            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = p116

            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('SetSpawnPoint')
        end
        function ShipTP(p117)
            local _TweenService2 = game:service('TweenService')
            local v119 = TweenInfo.new((game:GetService('Workspace').Boats:FindFirstChild(_G.Settings.Main['Select Boats']).VehicleSeat.CFrame.Position - p117.Position).Magnitude / 300, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear)

            tween = _TweenService2:Create(game:GetService('Workspace').Boats:FindFirstChild(_G.Settings.Main['Select Boats']).VehicleSeat, v119, {CFrame = p117})

            tween:Play()

            return {
                Stop = function(_)
                    tween:Cancel()
                end,
            }
        end
        function InMyNetWork(p120)
            if isnetworkowner then
                return isnetworkowner(p120)
            else
                return (p120.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).Magnitude <= 300
            end
        end

                        if v134 and game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer:DistanceFromCharacter(v134.Position) < 65 then
                            table.insert(v131, {v133, v134})

                            v132 = v132 or v134
                        end
                        if v132 and #v131 > 0 then
                            if _G.Settings.Config['Weapon Type'] ~= 'Gun' then
                                _RERegisterAttack:FireServer()
                                _RERegisterHit:FireServer(v132, v131)
                            else
                                local v135 = game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.ViewportSize.X / 2

                                game:GetService('VirtualInputManager'):SendMouseButtonEvent(v135, v136, 0, true, game, 1)
                                game:GetService('VirtualInputManager'):SendMouseButtonEvent(v135, v136, 0, false, game, 1)

                                    game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Modules.Net['RE/ShootGunEvent']:FireServer(v134.Position, {v134})
                                end
                            end
                        end
                    end
                end
            end

        function Com(p147, ...)
            local v148 = game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes:FindFirstChild('Comm' .. p147)

            if v148:IsA('RemoteEvent') then
                v148:FireServer(...)
            elseif v148:IsA('RemoteFunction') then
                v148:InvokeServer(...)
            end
        end

        local function u159(...)
            local v149 = {...}
            local v150 = v149[1]
            local v151 = nil

            if type(v150) ~= 'vector' then
                if type(v150) ~= 'userdata' then
                    if type(v150) == 'number' then
                        v151 = CFrame.new(unpack(v149)).p
                    end
                else
                    v151 = v150.Position
                end
            else
                v151 = v150
            end

            local v152 = nil
            local _huge = math.huge

            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Team then
                local v154, v155, v156 = pairs(game.Workspace._WorldOrigin.PlayerSpawns:FindFirstChild(tostring(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Team)):GetChildren())

                while true do
                    local v157

                    v156, v157 = v154(v155, v156)

                    if v156 == nil then
                        break
                    end

                    local _Magnitude = (v151 - v157:GetModelCFrame().p).Magnitude

                    if _Magnitude < _huge then
                        v152 = v157.Name
                        _huge = _Magnitude
                    end
                end

                if v152 then
                    return v152
                end
            end
        end

        function WaitHRP(p160)
            if p160 then
                return p160.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart', 9)
            end
        end

        local function u171(...)
            local v161 = {...}
            local v162 = v161[1]
            local u163 = nil

            if type(v162) ~= 'vector' then
                if type(v162) ~= 'userdata' then
                    if type(v162) == 'number' then
                        u163 = CFrame.new(unpack(v161))
                    end
                else
                    u163 = v162
                end
            else
                u163 = CFrame.new(v162)
            end
            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health == 0 then
                if tween then
                    tween:Cancel()
                end

                repeat
                    wait()
                until game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0

                wait(0.2)
            end

            local v164 = {}
            local _Magnitude2 = (u163.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).Magnitude

            if _Magnitude2 < 1000 then
                Speed = 345
            elseif _Magnitude2 >= 1000 then
                Speed = 300
            end
            if _G.Settings.Config['Bypass TP'] and (3000 < _Magnitude2 and (_G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Farm Dungeon'] and not (_G.Settings.Material.Enable or (_G.AutoGodhuman or _G.AutoRaid)))) and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Special Microchip') and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Special Microchip') and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Hallow Essence') and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Hallow Essence') and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Sweet Chalice') and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Sweet Chalice') and (NameMon ~= 'Fishman Commando' and NameMon ~= 'Fishman Warrior'))))))))) then
                pcall(function()
                    tween:Cancel()

                    fkwarp = false

                    if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Data:FindFirstChild('SpawnPoint').Value ~= tostring(u159(u163)) then
                        if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Data:FindFirstChild('LastSpawnPoint').Value ~= tostring(u159(u163)) then
                            if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0 then
                                if fkwarp == false then
                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = u163
                                end

                                fkwarp = true
                            end

                            wait(0.08)
                            game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid'):ChangeState(15)

                            repeat
                                wait()
                            until game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0

                            wait(0.1)
                            Com('F_', 'SetSpawnPoint')
                        else
                            game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid'):ChangeState(15)
                            wait(0.1)

                            repeat
                                wait()
                            until game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0
                        end
                    else
                        wait(0.1)
                        Com('F_', 'TeleportToSpawn')
                    end

                    wait(0.2)
                end)
            end
            if not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('PartTele') then
                local _Part = Instance.new('Part', game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character)

                _Part.Size = Vector3.new(1, 1, 1)
                _Part.Name = 'PartTele'
                _Part.Anchored = true
                _Part.Transparency = 1
                _Part.CanCollide = false
                _Part.CFrame = WaitHRP(game.Players.LocalPlayer).CFrame

                local v167 = _Part

                _Part.GetPropertyChangedSignal(v167, 'CFrame'):Connect(function()
                    task.wait()

                    WaitHRP(game.Players.LocalPlayer).CFrame = _Part.CFrame
                end)
            end

            local _TweenService3 = game:service('TweenService')
            local u169 = TweenInfo.new((u163.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).Magnitude / Speed, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear)
            local _, _ = pcall(function()
                local v170 = {CFrame = u163}

                tween = _TweenService3:Create(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.PartTele, u169, v170)

                tween:Play()
            end)

            function v164.Stop(_)
                tween:Cancel()
            end
            function v164.Wait(_)
                tween.Completed:Wait()
            end

            return v164
        end

        function toTargetP(...)
            local v172 = {...}
            local v173 = v172[1]
            local u174 = nil

            if type(v173) ~= 'vector' then
                if type(v173) ~= 'userdata' then
                    if type(v173) == 'number' then
                        u174 = CFrame.new(unpack(v172))
                    end
                else
                    u174 = v173
                end
            else
                u174 = CFrame.new(v173)
            end
            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health == 0 then
                if tween then
                    tween:Cancel()
                end

                repeat
                    wait()
                until game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0

                wait(0.2)
            end

            local v175 = {}
            local _Magnitude3 = (u174.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).Magnitude

            if _Magnitude3 < 1000 then
                Speed = 315
            elseif _Magnitude3 >= 1000 then
                Speed = 300
            end
            if not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('PartTele') then
                local _Part2 = Instance.new('Part', game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character)

                _Part2.Size = Vector3.new(1, 1, 1)

                _Part2.CanCollide = false

                    WaitHRP(game.Players.LocalPlayer).CFrame = _Part2.CFrame
                end)
            end

            local _TweenService4 = game:service('TweenService')
            local u180 = TweenInfo.new((u174.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).Magnitude / Speed, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear)
            local _, _ = pcall(function()
                local v181 = {CFrame = u174}

                tween = _TweenService4:Create(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.PartTele, u180, v181)

                tween:Play()
            end)

            function v175.Stop(_)
                tween:Cancel()
            end
            function v175.Wait(_)
                tween.Completed:Wait()
            end

            return v175
        end
        function TP(p182)
            Distance = (p182.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).Magnitude

            if Distance >= 10 then
                if Distance >= 170 then
                    if Distance >= 1000 then
                        if Distance >= 1000 then
                            Speed = 250
                        end
                    else
                        Speed = 350
                    end
                else
                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = p182
                    Speed = 350
                end
            else
                Speed = 1000
            end

            game:GetService('TweenService'):Create(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart, TweenInfo.new(Distance / Speed, Enum.EasingStyle.Linear), {CFrame = p182}):Play()
        end
        function InfinitiesEnergy()
            game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Energy.Changed:connect(function()
                if _G.InfinityEnergy then
                    game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Energy.Value = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Energy.MaxValue
                end
            end)
        end
        function getRoot(p183)
            return p183:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') or (p183:FindFirstChild('Torso') or p183:FindFirstChild('UpperTorso'))
        end

            if p184.Character:FindFirstChildOfClass('Humanoid').RigType == Enum.HumanoidRigType.R15 then
                return true
            end
        end

        repeat
            wait()
        until game.CoreGui:FindFirstChild('RobloxPromptGui')

        local _ = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer
        local _promptOverlay = game.CoreGui.RobloxPromptGui.promptOverlay
        local _TeleportService = game:GetService('TeleportService')

        _promptOverlay.ChildAdded:connect(function(p187)
            if _G.Settings.Config.Rejoin and p187.Name == 'ErrorPrompt' then
                wait(2)

                repeat
                    wait(2)
                    _TeleportService:Teleport(game.PlaceId)
                    wait(2)
                until false
            end
        end)

        local u188 = {}

        function Hop()
            local function v195()
                for v189 = 1, 100 do
                    local v190 = game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').__ServerBrowser:InvokeServer(v189)
                    local v191, v192, v193 = pairs(v190)

                    while true do
                        local v194

                        v193, v194 = v191(v192, v193)

                        if v193 == nil then
                            break
                        end
                        if v193 ~= game.JobId and v194.Count < 10 then
                            if not u188[v193] or tick() - u188[v193].Time > 600 then
                                u188[v193] = {
                                    Time = tick(),
                                }

                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').__ServerBrowser:InvokeServer('teleport', v193)

                                return true
                            end
                            if tick() - u188[v193].Time > 3600 then
                                u188[v193] = nil
                            end
                        end
                    end
                end

                return false
            end

            if not getgenv().Loaded then
                local v196, v197, v198 = pairs(game.CoreGui.RobloxPromptGui.promptOverlay:GetChildren())

                local function v200(p199)
                    while true do
                        wait()

                        if p199.Name == 'ErrorPrompt' then
                            if p199.Visible and p199.TitleFrame.ErrorTitle.Text == 'Teleport failed' then
                                Hop()
                            end

                            p199:GetPropertyChangedSignal('Visible'):Connect(function()
                                if p199.Visible and p199.TitleFrame.ErrorTitle.Text == 'Teleport failed' then
                                    Hop()
                                end
                            end)
                        end
                        if Hop() then
                            return
                        end
                    end
                end

                while true do
                    local v201

                    v198, v201 = v196(v197, v198)

                    if v198 == nil then
                        break
                    end

                    v200(v201)
                end

                game.CoreGui.RobloxPromptGui.promptOverlay.ChildAdded:Connect(v200)

                getgenv().Loaded = true
            end

            while not v195() do
                wait()
            end
        end
        function RemoveFruit(p202)
            return p202:gsub(' Fruit', '')
        end
        function comma_value(p203)
            repeat
                local v204

                p203, v204 = string.gsub(p203, '^(-?%d+)(%d%d%d)', '%1,%2')
            until v204 == 0

            return p203
        end

        _G.CheckFruitLocal1M = false

        function CheckFruit1M()
            local v205, v206, v207 = pairs(game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild('Remotes').CommF_:InvokeServer('getInventoryFruits'))

            while true do
                local v208

                v207, v208 = v205(v206, v207)

                if v207 == nil then
                    break
                end
                if v208.Price >= 1000000 then
                    _G.CheckFruitLocal1M = true
                end
            end
        end
        function GetFightingStyle(p209)
            ReturnText = ''

            local v210, v211, v212 = pairs(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:GetChildren())

            while true do
                local v213

                v212, v213 = v210(v211, v212)

                if v212 == nil then
                    break
                end
                if v213:IsA('Tool') and v213.ToolTip == p209 then
                    ReturnText = v213.Name
                end
            end

            local v214, v215, v216 = pairs(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:GetChildren())

            while true do
                local v217

                v216, v217 = v214(v215, v216)

                if v216 == nil then
                    break
                end
                if v217:IsA('Tool') and v217.ToolTip == p209 then
                    ReturnText = v217.Name
                end
            end

            return ReturnText == '' and 'Not Have' or ReturnText
        end
        function CheckMasteryWeapon(p218, p219)
            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild(p218) then
                if tonumber(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild(p218).Level.Value) < tonumber(p219) then
                    return 'true DownTo'
                end
                if tonumber(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild(p218).Level.Value) >= tonumber(p219) then
                    return 'true UpTo'
                end
            end
            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(p218) then
                if tonumber(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(p218).Level.Value) < tonumber(p219) then
                    return 'true DownTo'
                end
                if tonumber(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(p218).Level.Value) >= tonumber(p219) then
                    return 'true UpTo'
                end
            end

            return 'else'
        end

            while true do

                if v223 == nil then
                    break
                end
                if type(v224) == 'table' and (v224.Type == 'Sword' and v224.Name == p220) then

                end
            end

            return false
        end

        spawn(function()
            local v242 = getrawmetatable(game)
            local ___namecall = v242.__namecall

            setreadonly(v242, false)

            v242.__namecall = newcclosure(function(...)
                local v244 = getnamecallmethod()
                local v245 = {...}

                if tostring(v244) ~= 'FireServer' or (tostring(v245[1]) ~= 'RemoteEvent' or (tostring(v245[2]) == 'true' or (tostring(v245[2]) == 'false' or not UseSkillMasteryDevilFruit))) then
                    return ___namecall(...)
                end
                if type(v245[2]) ~= 'vector' then
                    v245[2] = CFrame.new(PositionSkillMasteryDevilFruit)
                else
                    v245[2] = PositionSkillMasteryDevilFruit
                end

                return ___namecall(unpack(v245))
            end)
        end)

        function CheckQuestBoss()
            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Saber Expert' then
                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'The Saw' then
                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Greybeard' then
                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Mob Leader' then
                            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'The Gorilla King' then
                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Bobby [Lv. 55]' then
                                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Yeti [Lv. 110]' then
                                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Vice Admiral' then
                                            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Warden' then
                                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Chief Warden' then
                                                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Swan' then
                                                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Magma Admiral' then
                                                            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Fishman Lord' then
                                                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Wysper' then
                                                                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Thunder God' then
                                                                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Cyborg' then
                                                                            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Don Swan' then
                                                                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Diamond' then
                                                                                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Jeremy' then
                                                                                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Fajita' then
                                                                                            if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Smoke Admiral' then
                                                                                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Awakened Ice Admiral' then
                                                                                                    if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Tide Keeper' then
                                                                                                        if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Cursed Captain' then

                                                                                                                if _G.SelectBoss ~= 'Order' then

        CheckQuestBoss()

        AttackRandomType = 1

        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                AttackRandomType = math.random(1, 5)

                wait(0.3)
            end
        end)

        function isnil(p260)
            return p260 == nil
        end

        local function u262(p261)
            return math.floor(tonumber(p261) + 0.5)
        end

        Number = math.random(1, 1000000)

        function UpdateEspPlayer()
            local v263, v264, v265 = pairs(game:GetService('Players'):GetChildren())

            while true do
                local u266

                v265, u266 = v263(v264, v265)

                if v265 == nil then
                    break
                end

                pcall(function()
                    if not isnil(u266.Character) then
                        if ESPPlayer then
                            if isnil(u266.Character.Head) or u266.Character.Head:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number) then
                                u266.Character.Head['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = u266.Name .. ' | ' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u266.Character.Head.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M\nHealth : ' .. u262(u266.Character.Humanoid.Health * 100 / u266.Character.Humanoid.MaxHealth) .. '%'
                            else
                                local _BillboardGui = Instance.new('BillboardGui', u266.Character.Head)

                                _BillboardGui.Name = 'NameEsp' .. Number
                                _BillboardGui.ExtentsOffset = Vector3.new(0, 1, 0)
                                _BillboardGui.Size = UDim2.new(1, 200, 1, 30)
                                _BillboardGui.Adornee = u266.Character.Head
                                _BillboardGui.AlwaysOnTop = true

                                local _TextLabel4 = Instance.new('TextLabel', _BillboardGui)

                                _TextLabel4.Font = Enum.Font.Code
                                _TextLabel4.FontSize = 'Size14'
                                _TextLabel4.TextWrapped = true
                                _TextLabel4.Text = u266.Name .. ' \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u266.Character.Head.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                                _TextLabel4.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0)
                                _TextLabel4.TextYAlignment = 'Top'
                                _TextLabel4.BackgroundTransparency = 1
                                _TextLabel4.TextStrokeTransparency = 0.5
                                _TextLabel4.TextColor3 = Color3.new(255, 255, 255)
                            end
                        elseif u266.Character.Head:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number) then
                            u266.Character.Head:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number):Destroy()
                        end
                    end
                end)
            end
        end
        function UpdateIslandESP()
            local v269, v270, v271 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:GetChildren())

            while true do
                local u272

                v271, u272 = v269(v270, v271)

                if v271 == nil then
                    break
                end

                pcall(function()
                    if IslandESP then
                        if u272.Name ~= 'Sea' then
                            if u272:FindFirstChild('NameEsp') then
                                u272.NameEsp.TextLabel.Text = u272.Name .. '   \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u272.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                            else
                                local _BillboardGui2 = Instance.new('BillboardGui', u272)

                                _BillboardGui2.Name = 'NameEsp'
                                _BillboardGui2.ExtentsOffset = Vector3.new(0, 1, 0)
                                _BillboardGui2.Size = UDim2.new(1, 200, 1, 30)
                                _BillboardGui2.Adornee = u272
                                _BillboardGui2.AlwaysOnTop = true

                                local _TextLabel5 = Instance.new('TextLabel', _BillboardGui2)

                                _TextLabel5.Font = Enum.Font.Code
                                _TextLabel5.FontSize = 'Size14'
                                _TextLabel5.TextWrapped = true
                                _TextLabel5.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0)
                                _TextLabel5.TextYAlignment = 'Top'
                                _TextLabel5.BackgroundTransparency = 1
                                _TextLabel5.TextStrokeTransparency = 0.5
                                _TextLabel5.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(80, 245, 245)
                            end
                        end
                    elseif u272:FindFirstChild('NameEsp') then
                        u272:FindFirstChild('NameEsp'):Destroy()
                    end
                end)
            end
        end
        function UpdateChestEsp()
            local v275, v276, v277 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace'):GetChildren())

            while true do
                local u278

                v277, u278 = v275(v276, v277)

                if v277 == nil then
                    break
                end

                pcall(function()
                    if string.find(u278.Name, 'Chest') then
                        if ChestESP then
                            if string.find(u278.Name, 'Chest') then
                                if u278:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number) then
                                    if u278.Name == 'Chest1' then
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = 'Silver Chest' .. ' \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u278.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(192, 192, 192)
                                    end
                                    if u278.Name == 'Chest2' then
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = 'Gold Chest' .. ' \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u278.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 215, 0)
                                    end
                                    if u278.Name == 'Chest3' then
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = 'Platinum Chest' .. ' \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u278.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                                        u278['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 170, 204)
                                    end

                                    u278.Handle['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = u278.Name .. '   \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u278.Handle.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                                else
                                    local _BillboardGui3 = Instance.new('BillboardGui', u278)

                                    _BillboardGui3.Name = 'NameEsp' .. Number
                                    _BillboardGui3.ExtentsOffset = Vector3.new(0, 1, 0)
                                    _BillboardGui3.Size = UDim2.new(1, 200, 1, 30)
                                    _BillboardGui3.Adornee = u278
                                    _BillboardGui3.AlwaysOnTop = true

                                    local _TextLabel6 = Instance.new('TextLabel', _BillboardGui3)

                                    _TextLabel6.Font = Enum.Font.Code
                                    _TextLabel6.FontSize = 'Size14'
                                    _TextLabel6.TextWrapped = true
                                    _TextLabel6.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0)
                                    _TextLabel6.TextYAlignment = 'Top'
                                    _TextLabel6.BackgroundTransparency = 1
                                    _TextLabel6.TextStrokeTransparency = 0.5
                                end
                            end
                        elseif u278:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number) then
                            u278:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number):Destroy()
                        end
                    end
                end)
            end
        end

        function UpdateFlowerEsp()
            local v287, v288, v289 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace'):GetChildren())

            while true do
                local u290

                v289, u290 = v287(v288, v289)

                if v289 == nil then
                    break
                end

                pcall(function()
                    if u290.Name == 'Flower2' or u290.Name == 'Flower1' then
                        if FlowerESP then
                            if u290:FindFirstChild('NameEsp' .. Number) then
                                u290['NameEsp' .. Number].TextLabel.Text = u290.Name .. '   \n' .. u262((game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Head.Position - u290.Position).Magnitude / 3) .. ' M'
                            else

                            end

                        end
                    end
                end)
            end
        end

        Time = v102.Main:AddParagraph({
            Title = '',
            Content = '',
        })

        function UpdateTime()
            local _t2 = os.date('*t')
            local v312 = _t2.hour % 24
            local v313 = v312 < 12 and 'AM' or 'PM'
            local __02i02i02is2 = string.format('%02i:%02i:%02i %s', (v312 - 1) % 12 + 1, _t2.min, _t2.sec, v313)
            local __02d02d04d2 = string.format('%02d/%02d/%04d', _t2.day, _t2.month, _t2.year)
            local _LocalizationService2 = game:GetService('LocalizationService')
            local _LocalPlayer3 = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer
            local _ = _LocalPlayer3.Name
            local _, v318 = pcall(function()
                return _LocalizationService2:GetCountryRegionForPlayerAsync(_LocalPlayer3)
            end)

            Time:SetTitle(__02d02d04d2 .. ' - ' .. __02i02i02is2 .. ' [ ' .. v318 .. ' ]')
        end

        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    UpdateTime()
                end)
            end
        end)
        game:GetService('RunService').RenderStepped:Connect(function(p319)
            local v320 = math.floor(workspace.DistributedGameTime + 0.5)
            local v321 = math.floor(v320 / 3600) % 24
            local v322 = math.floor(v320 / 60) % 60
            local v323 = math.floor(v320 / 1) % 60

            Time:SetDesc('Hour : ' .. v321 .. '  |  Minute : ' .. v322 .. '  |  Second : ' .. v323 .. '\n[Ping] : ' .. game:GetService('Stats').Network.ServerStatsItem['Data Ping']:GetValueString(math.floor(2)) .. '   [FPS] : ' .. math.floor(2 / p319))
        end)

                        if v326 == nil then
                            break
                        end
                        if v326 == 12 then
                            PlayerStatus:SetTitle('Players :' .. ' ' .. v326 .. ' / 12 (Max)')
                        elseif v326 == 1 then
                            PlayerStatus:SetTitle('Player :' .. ' ' .. v326 .. ' / 12')
                        else
                            PlayerStatus:SetTitle('Players :' .. ' ' .. v326 .. ' / 12')
                        end
                    end

            end
        end)

        v102.Main:AddButton({
            Title = 'Hop to Lower Player',
            Description = 'it will Teleport to Lower People on The Server',
            Callback = function()
                local v328 = game
                local _Workspace = v328.Workspace
                local _Lighting = v328.Lighting
                local _Terrain = _Workspace.Terrain

                _Terrain.WaterWaveSize = 0
                _Terrain.WaterWaveSpeed = 0
                _Terrain.WaterReflectance = 0
                _Terrain.WaterTransparency = 0
                _Lighting.GlobalShadows = false
                _Lighting.FogEnd = 9000000000
                _Lighting.Brightness = 0
                settings().Rendering.QualityLevel = 'Level01'

                local v332, v333, v334 = pairs(v328:GetDescendants())
                local v335 = true

                while true do
                    local v336

                    v334, v336 = v332(v333, v334)

                    if v334 == nil then
                        break
                    end
                    if v336:IsA('Part') or (v336:IsA('Union') or (v336:IsA('CornerWedgePart') or v336:IsA('TrussPart'))) then
                        v336.Material = 'Plastic'
                        v336.Reflectance = 0
                    elseif v336:IsA('Decal') or v336:IsA('Texture') and v335 then
                        v336.Transparency = 1
                    elseif v336:IsA('ParticleEmitter') or v336:IsA('Trail') then
                        v336.Lifetime = NumberRange.new(0)
                    elseif v336:IsA('Explosion') then
                        v336.BlastPressure = 1
                        v336.BlastRadius = 1
                    elseif v336:IsA('Fire') or (v336:IsA('SpotLight') or (v336:IsA('Smoke') or v336:IsA('Sparkles'))) then
                        v336.Enabled = false
                    elseif v336:IsA('MeshPart') then
                        v336.Material = 'Plastic'
                        v336.Reflectance = 0
                        v336.TextureID = 1.0385902758728955e16
                    end
                end

                local v337, v338, v339 = pairs(_Lighting:GetChildren())

                while true do
                    local v340

                    v339, v340 = v337(v338, v339)

                    if v339 == nil then
                        break
                    end
                    if v340:IsA('BlurEffect') or (v340:IsA('SunRaysEffect') or (v340:IsA('ColorCorrectionEffect') or (v340:IsA('BloomEffect') or v340:IsA('DepthOfFieldEffect')))) then
                        v340.Enabled = false
                    end
                end
            end,
        })

        })

        local v343, v344, v345 = pairs(_GetFruits)

        local function v349(p346)
            local v347 = tostring(p346)

            repeat
                local v348

                v347, v348 = v347:gsub('^(-?%d+)(%d%d%d)', '%1,%2')
                k = v348
            until k == 0

            return v347
        end

        local u350 = ''

        while true do
            local v351

            v345, v351 = v343(v344, v345)

            if v345 == nil then
                break
            end
            if v351.OnSale == true then
                local v352 = v349(v351.Price)

                u350 = u350 .. v351.Name .. ' - $' .. v352 .. '\n'
            end
        end

        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    MirageFruit:SetDesc(u350)
                end)
            end
        end)
        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    if game:GetService('Lighting').Sky.MoonTextureId ~= 'http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=9709149431' then
                        if game:GetService('Lighting').Sky.MoonTextureId ~= 'http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=9709149052' then
                            if game:GetService('Lighting').Sky.MoonTextureId ~= 'http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=9709143733' then
                                if game:GetService('Lighting').Sky.MoonTextureId ~= 'http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=9709150401' then
                                    if game:GetService('Lighting').Sky.MoonTextureId ~= 'http://www.roblox.com/asset/?id=9709149680' then
                                        FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 0% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                                    else
                                        FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 15% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                                    end
                                else
                                    FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 25% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                                end
                            else
                                FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 50% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                            end
                        else
                            FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 75% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                        end
                    else
                        FullMoonStatus:SetDesc('\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd}\u{fffd} : Full Moon 100% (' .. tostring(game:GetService('Lighting').TimeOfDay) .. ')')
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)
        spawn(function()
            pcall(function()
                while wait() do
                    if World3 then
                        if game.Workspace._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Mirage Island') then
                            MirageStatus:SetDesc('Mirage Island is Spawning')
                        else
                            MirageStatus:SetDesc('Not Spawn')
                        end
                        if game.Workspace._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Kitsune Island') then

                        else
                            KitsuneStatus:SetDesc('Not Spawn')
                        end
                    else
                        KitsuneStatus:SetDesc('Go To World 3')
                        MirageStatus:SetDesc('Go To World 3')
                    end

                    local v353, v354, v355 = pairs(game.Workspace:GetChildren())

                    while true do
                        local v356

                        v355, v356 = v353(v354, v355)

                        if v355 == nil then
                            break
                        end
                        if string.find(v356.Name, 'Fruit') then
                            FruitStatus:SetDesc(v356.Name)
                        else
                            FruitStatus:SetDesc('Not Spawn')
                        end
                    end
                end
            end)
        end)
        spawn(function()
            while wait() do

        _OthersSetting:AddButton({
            Title = 'FPS Boost',
            Description = 'it will Remove all texture make your game less Lag',
            Callback = function()
                local v382 = game
                local _Workspace2 = v382.Workspace
                local _Lighting2 = v382.Lighting
                local _Terrain2 = _Workspace2.Terrain

                _Terrain2.WaterWaveSize = 0
                _Terrain2.WaterWaveSpeed = 0
                _Terrain2.WaterReflectance = 0
                _Terrain2.WaterTransparency = 0
                _Lighting2.GlobalShadows = false
                _Lighting2.FogEnd = 9000000000
                _Lighting2.Brightness = 0
                settings().Rendering.QualityLevel = 'Level01'

                local v386, v387, v388 = pairs(v382:GetDescendants())
                local v389 = true

                while true do
                    local v390

                    v388, v390 = v386(v387, v388)

                    if v388 == nil then
                        break
                    end
                    if v390:IsA('Part') or (v390:IsA('Union') or (v390:IsA('CornerWedgePart') or v390:IsA('TrussPart'))) then
                        v390.Material = 'Plastic'
                        v390.Reflectance = 0
                    elseif v390:IsA('Decal') or v390:IsA('Texture') and v389 then
                        v390.Transparency = 1
                    elseif v390:IsA('ParticleEmitter') or v390:IsA('Trail') then
                        v390.Lifetime = NumberRange.new(0)
                    elseif v390:IsA('Explosion') then
                        v390.BlastPressure = 1
                        v390.BlastRadius = 1
                    elseif v390:IsA('Fire') or (v390:IsA('SpotLight') or (v390:IsA('Smoke') or v390:IsA('Sparkles'))) then
                        v390.Enabled = false
                    elseif v390:IsA('MeshPart') then
                        v390.Material = 'Plastic'
                        v390.Reflectance = 0
                        v390.TextureID = 1.0385902758728955e16
                    end
                end

                local v391, v392, v393 = pairs(_Lighting2:GetChildren())

                while true do
                    local v394

                    v393, v394 = v391(v392, v393)

                    if v393 == nil then
                        break
                    end
                    if v394:IsA('BlurEffect') or (v394:IsA('SunRaysEffect') or (v394:IsA('ColorCorrectionEffect') or (v394:IsA('BloomEffect') or v394:IsA('DepthOfFieldEffect')))) then
                        v394.Enabled = false
                    end
                end
            end,
        })

        function CheckNotifyComplete()
            local v404, v405, v406 = pairs(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.PlayerGui:FindFirstChild('Notifications'):GetChildren())

            while true do
                local u407

                v406, u407 = v404(v405, v406)

                if v406 == nil then
                    break
                end
                if u407.Name == 'NotificationTemplate' and string.lower(u407.Text):find('quest completed') then
                    pcall(function()
                        u407:Destroy()
                    end)

                    return true
                end
            end

            return false
        end

        local u408 = false
        local u409 = false
        local u410 = Name
        local u411 = NameMon

        task.spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    if not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Select Monster'] and (not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] and (not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Mastery'] or _G.Settings.Main['Type Mastery'] ~= 'Quest')) and (not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Mastery'] or _G.Settings.Main['Type Mastery'] ~= 'No Quest') then
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Config['Double Quest'] then
                        if u409 ~= true then
                            CheckQuest()

                            u410 = Name
                            u411 = NameMon

                            spawn(function()
                                pcall(function()
                                    if u408 == false and (CheckNotifyComplete() and _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level']) then
                                        u408 = true

                                        while wait(0.5) do
                                            u409 = true

                                            if CheckNotifyComplete() or _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] == false then
                                                break
                                            end
                                        end

                                        u409 = false
                                        u408 = false
                                    end
                                end)
                            end)
                        elseif LevelFarm and tonumber(LevelFarm - 1) ~= 0 then
                            CheckOldQuest(tonumber(LevelFarm - 1))
                        end
                    else
                        CheckQuest()
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Mastery'] then
                    end

                    GetQuestTitle = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest.Container.QuestTitle.Title
                    GetQuest = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest

                    local _ = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.Level.Value

                    if not string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) then
                        game.ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild('Remotes').CommF_:InvokeServer('AbandonQuest')
                    end
                    if GetQuest.Visible == false then
                        StartMagnet = false
                        FastAttack = false
                        Questtween = u171(CFrameQuest.Position, CFrameQuest)

                        if World1 and (NameMon == 'Fishman Commando' or NameMon == 'Fishman Warrior') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                            if Questtween then
                                Questtween:Stop()
                            end

                            wait(0.5)
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(61163.8515625, 11.6796875, 1819.7841796875))
                        elseif World1 and (NameMon ~= 'Fishman Commando' and NameMon ~= 'Fishman Warrior') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                            if Questtween then
                                Questtween:Stop()
                            end

                            wait(0.5)
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(3864.8515625, 6.6796875, -1926.7841796875))
                        elseif World2 and string.find(Name, 'Ship') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 30000 then
                            if Questtween then
                                Questtween:Stop()
                            end

                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(923.21252441406, 126.9760055542, 32852.83203125))
                        elseif World2 and not string.find(Name, 'Ship') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 30000 then
                            if Questtween then
                                Questtween:Stop()
                            end

                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-6508.5581054688, 89.034996032715, -132.83953857422))
                        elseif (CFrameQuest.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 250 then
                            if Questtween then
                                Questtween:Stop()
                            end

                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = CFrameQuest

                            wait(1)

                    if not string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, QuestName) then
                    end
                    if true then
                        wait()

                        if (v462.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150 then
                            if v462:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v462:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v462.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150) then
                                if FarmtoTarget then
                                    FarmtoTarget:Stop()
                                end

                                StartMagnet = true
                                PosMon = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame

                                if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value >= 150 then
                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                                end
                                if AttackRandomType ~= 1 then
                                    if AttackRandomType ~= 2 then
                                        if AttackRandomType ~= 3 then
                                            if AttackRandomType ~= 4 then
                                                if AttackRandomType ~= 5 then
                                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 1)
                                                else
                                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(-30, 1, 0)
                                                end
                                            else
                                                game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(30, 1, 0)
                                            end
                                        else
                                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(1, 1, -30)
                                        end
                                    else
                                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 1, 30)
                                    end
                                else
                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 1)
                                end

                                FastAttack = true

                                EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                            end
                        else
                            FarmtoTarget = u171(v462.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 1))
                        end
                    end
                    if game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(NameMon) and (_G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] ~= false and (_G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, QuestName) and (v462.Humanoid.Health > 0 and (v462.Parent and GetQuest.Visible ~= false))))) then
                    end

                    FastAttack = false
                    StartMagnet = false

                    Com('F_', 'AbandonQuest')

                    local v462

                    v461, v462 = v459(v460, v461)

                    if v461 == nil then
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (v462.Name == NameMon and (v462:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v462:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and v462.Humanoid.Health > 0))) then
                    else
                    end
                    if string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) then
                    end

                    Com('F_', 'AbandonQuest')
                    wait()

                    FarmtoTarget = u171(v463.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 0))

                    if v463:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v463:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v463.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 250) then
                        if FarmtoTarget then
                            FarmtoTarget:Stop()
                        end

                        AutoHaki()
                        EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])

                        StartMagnet = true
                        FastAttack = true
                        v463.HumanoidRootPart.Transparency = 1
                        v463.Humanoid.JumpPower = 0
                        v463.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0
                        v463.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false

                        v463.Humanoid:ChangeState(11)
                        v463.Humanoid:ChangeState(14)

                        if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                            game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                            game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 670), workspace.CurrentCamera.CFrame)
                        end

                        PosMon = v463.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame

                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value >= 150 then
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                        elseif game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Death Step') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Death Step').Level.Value >= 400 then
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                        end

                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v463.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 0)
                    end
                    if game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(v463.Name) and (_G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) and (v463.Humanoid.Health > 0 and (v463.Parent and GetQuest.Visible ~= false)))) then
                    end

                    StartMagnet = false
                    FastAttack = false

                    while true do
                        local v463

                        v444, v463 = v442(v443, v444)

                        if v444 == nil then
                        end
                        if string.find(v463.Name, 'kissed Warrior') then
                            break
                        end
                        if string.find(v463.Name, 'kissed Warrior') == nil then
                            StartMagnet = false
                            FastAttack = false

                            if not string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) then
                                Com('F_', 'AbandonQuest')
                            end

                            Modstween = u171(CFrameMon.Position, CFrameMon)

                            if World1 and (NameMon == 'Fishman Commando' or NameMon == 'Fishman Warrior') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(61163.8515625, 11.6796875, 1819.7841796875))
                            elseif World1 and (NameMon ~= 'Fishman Commando' and NameMon ~= 'Fishman Warrior') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(3864.8515625, 6.6796875, -1926.7841796875))
                            elseif World2 and string.find(Name, 'Ship') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 30000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(923.21252441406, 126.9760055542, 32852.83203125))
                            elseif World2 and not string.find(Name, 'Ship') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 30000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-6508.5581054688, 89.034996032715, -132.83953857422))
                            elseif (CFrameMon.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 250 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = CFrameMon
                            end
                        end
                    end

                    if game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(v463.Name) and (_G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (v463.Name == v463.Name and (v463:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v463:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and v463.Humanoid.Health > 0)))) then
                    else
                    end
                    if string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) then
                    end

                    Com('F_', 'AbandonQuest')
                    wait()

                    FarmtoTarget = u171(v464.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 0))

                    if v464:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v464:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v464.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 250) then
                        if FarmtoTarget then
                            FarmtoTarget:Stop()
                        end

                        AutoHaki()

                        if not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(_G.SelectWeapon) then
                            wait()
                            EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                        end

                        StartMagnet = true
                        FastAttack = true

                        if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                            game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                            game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 670), workspace.CurrentCamera.CFrame)
                        end

                        v464.HumanoidRootPart.Transparency = 1
                        v464.Humanoid.JumpPower = 0
                        v464.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0
                        v464.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false

                        v464.Humanoid:ChangeState(11)
                        v464.Humanoid:ChangeState(14)

                        PosMon = v464.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame

                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value >= 150 then
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                        end

                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v464.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 0)
                    end
                    if game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(NameMon) and (_G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (string.find(GetQuestTitle.Text, NameMon) and (v464.Humanoid.Health > 0 and (v464.Parent and GetQuest.Visible ~= false)))) then
                    end

                    StartMagnet = false
                    FastAttack = false

                    local v464

                    v447, v464 = v445(v446, v447)

                    if v447 == nil then
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Main['Fast Farm Level'] and (v464.Name == NameMon and (v464:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v464:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and v464.Humanoid.Health > 0))) then
                    else
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)
