        local u513 = false
        local u514 = false
        local u515 = false
        local u516 = false
        local u517 = false
        local u518 = false

        function GetAllMeleeFarm()
            if u513 == false then
                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                    'BuySuperhuman',
                }))

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Superhuman', 400) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u513 = true
                end
            end

            wait(0.5)

            if u514 == false then
                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyElectricClaw')

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Electric Claw', 400) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u514 = true
                end
            end

            wait(0.5)

            if u515 == false then
                game.ReplicatedStorage.Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyDragonTalon')

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Dragon Talon', 400) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u515 = true
                end
            end

            wait(0.5)

            if u516 == false then
                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                    'BuySharkmanKarate',
                }))

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Sharkman Karate', 400) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u516 = true
                end
            end

            wait(0.5)

            if u517 == false then
                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                    'BuyDeathStep',
                }))

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Death Step', 400) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u517 = true
                end
            end
            if u518 == false then
                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                    'BuyGodhuman',
                }))

                if CheckMasteryWeapon('Godhuman', 350) == 'true UpTo' then
                    u518 = true
                end
            end
        end

        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    if _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Auto Superhuman'] and game.Players.LocalPlayer:FindFirstChild('WeaponAssetCache') then
                        if not (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Combat') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Combat') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Electro') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Electro') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Fishman Karate') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Fishman Karate') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Dragon Claw') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Dragon Claw') or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Superhuman') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Superhuman')))))))))))) then
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyBlackLeg')
                        end

                        _G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'] = GetFightingStyle('Melee')

                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Combat') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Combat') then
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyBlackLeg')
                        end
                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('BlackLeg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('BlackLeg').Level.Value >= 300 then
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyElectro')
                        end
                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Fishman Karate') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Fishman Karate').Level.Value >= 300 then
                            HaveDragonClaw = game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                                'BlackbeardReward',
                                'DragonClaw',
                                '2',
                            }))

                            if _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Auto Superhuman'] and (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.Fragments.Value <= 1500 and HaveDragonClaw == 0) then
                                if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.Level.Value > 1100 then
                                    _G.Settings.Dungeon.Chip = 'Flame'
                                    _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Farm Dungeon'] = true

                                    if Auto_Farm_Level then
                                        _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] = false
                                    end
                                end
                            else
                                _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Farm Dungeon'] = false

                                if Auto_Farm_Level then
                                    _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] = true
                                end

                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                                    'BlackbeardReward',
                                    'DragonClaw',
                                    '2',
                                }))

                                _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Farm Dungeon'] = false

                                if Auto_Farm_Level then
                                    _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] = true
                                end
                            end
                        end
                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Dragon Claw') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Dragon Claw').Level.Value >= 300 then
                            Auto_Farm_Level = _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level']

                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer(unpack({
                                'BuySuperhuman',
                            }))
                        end
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)
        _FightingStyle:AddToggle('DeathStep', {
            Title = 'Auto Learn DeathStep',
            Default = _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Death Step'],
        })
        _Options.DeathStep:OnChanged(function()
            _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Death Step'] = _Options.DeathStep.Value

            if _Options.DeathStep.Value == false then
                wait()
                u171(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                wait()
            end

            SaveSettings()
        end)
        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    if not _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Death Step'] then
                        return
                    end
                    if (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value < 400) and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value < 400) then
                        game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyBlackLeg')
                    end
                    if game:GetService('Workspace').Map.IceCastle.Hall.LibraryDoor.PhoeyuDoor.Transparency ~= 0 then
                        game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyDeathStep')
                    end
                    if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Library Key') or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Library Key') then
                        EquipWeapon('Library Key')

                        repeat
                            wait()
                            u171(CFrame.new(6371.2001953125, 296.63433837890625, -6841.18115234375))
                        until (CFrame.new(6371.2001953125, 296.63433837890625, -6841.18115234375).Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).Magnitude <= 3 or not _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Death Step']

                        if (CFrame.new(6371.2001953125, 296.63433837890625, -6841.18115234375).Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).Magnitude <= 3 then
                            wait(1.2)
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyDeathStep', true)
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyDeathStep')
                            wait(0.5)
                        end
                    end
                    if (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value < 400) and (not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value < 400) then
                    end
                    if not (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral') or game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral')) then
                        if not game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral') then
                            wait(3)
                            u98:Notify({
                                Title = 'Thunder Notification',
                                Content = 'Boss Status',
                                SubContent = 'Awakened Ice Admiral not Spawn yet !',
                                Duration = 3,
                            })
                        end
                    end
                    if not game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral') then
                        if game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral') then
                            u171(game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Awakened Ice Admiral').HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                        end
                    end

                    local v519, v520, v521 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:GetChildren())

                    wait()

                    if game.Workspace.Enemies:FindFirstChild(v522.Name) then
                        if (v522.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 200 then
                            if (v522.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 200 then
                                if Farmtween then
                                    Farmtween:Stop()
                                end

                                FastAttack = true

                                AutoHaki()

                                if not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon']) then
                                    wait()
                                    EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                                end
                                if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                                    game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                                    game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 672))
                                end

                                v522.Humanoid.JumpPower = 0
                                v522.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0
                                v522.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false

                                v522.Humanoid:ChangeState(11)
                                u171(v522.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 0))

                                if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value >= 150 then
                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                                end
                            end
                        else
                            Farmtween = u171(v522.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                        end
                    end
                    if v522.Parent and (v522.Humanoid.Health > 0 and _G.Settings.FightingStyle['Death Step'] ~= false) and not (game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Library Key') or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Library Key')) then
                    end

                    FastAttack = false

                    local v522

                    v521, v522 = v519(v520, v521)

                    if v521 == nil then
                    end
                    if v522.Name ~= 'Awakened Ice Admiral' then
                    else
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)

                        game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyGodhuman')

                        _G.Settings.FightingStyle.Godhuman = false
                    end

                        BuyDragonTalon = tonumber(game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuyDragonTalon', true))

                        if BuyDragonTalon and BuyDragonTalon == 1 then
                            HasTalon = true
                        end
                    end
                    if not HasSuperhuman then
                        BuySuperhuman = tonumber(game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BuySuperhuman', true))

                            HasSuperhuman = true
                        end

                        end

                        end

                                                                                wait(0.1)

                                                                            end

                                                                            if MasterySkill.V.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X >= 1 or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value == false then
                                                                            end
                                                                        end
                                                                    end
                                                                    if not u638:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and u638:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') then
                                                                    end

                                                                    end
                                                                end

                                                                FastAttack = false
                                                            end
                                                        end
                                                        if not game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(u638.Name) or (not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Mastery'] or (u638.Humanoid.Health <= 0 or not u638.Parent)) then
                                                            return
                                                        end
                                                    end
                                                end)

                                                StartMagnet = false
                                                FastAttack = false
                                            end
                                        else

                                            StartMagnet = false

                                            end
                                        end
                                    end

                                        local u643

                                        if v642 == nil then
                                            break
                                        end

                                                                end

                                                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = u643.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Main['Distance Mastery'], 5)

                                                    end

                                            end)

                                    StartMagnet = false

                                    elseif World1 and (NameMon == 'Shanda' or (NameMon == 'Royal Squad' or NameMon == 'Royal Soldier')) and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 5000 then

                                        if Modstween then

                                        end

                                        game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-6508.5581054688, 89.034996032715, -132.83953857422))

                            end
                        else

                            FastAttack = false
                            Questtween = u171(CFrameQuest.Position, CFrameQuest)

                            if World1 and (NameMon == 'Fishman Commando' or NameMon == 'Fishman Warrior') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then

                                    Questtween:Stop()

                                if Questtween then
                                    Questtween:Stop()
                                end

                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(923.21252441406, 126.9760055542, 32852.83203125))
                            elseif World2 and not string.find(Name, 'Ship') and (CFrameQuest.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 30000 then
                                if Questtween then

                                end

                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-6508.5581054688, 89.034996032715, -132.83953857422))
                            elseif (CFrameQuest.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 250 then
                                if Questtween then
                                    Questtween:Stop()
                                end

                                game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = CFrameQuest

                                wait(1)

                                if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('Humanoid').Health > 0 then
                                    Com('F_', 'StartQuest', QuestName, LevelQuest)
                                    Com('F_', 'SetSpawnPoint')
                                end
                            end
                        end
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)

                                    repeat
                                        wait()

                                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v673.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 150, 0)
                                    until MasterySkill.X.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X <= 1 or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value == false
                                end
                                if _G.Settings.Main['Use Skill'].C == true and (MasterySkill.C.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X <= 1 and (v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v673:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v673.Humanoid.Health > 0 and DevilFruitMastery >= MasteryDevilFruit.Lvl.C)))) then
                                    wait()

                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v673.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Main['Distance Mastery'], 5)

                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'C', false, game)

                                    if _G.Settings.Main['Hold Skill'].C ~= true then
                                        wait(0.1)
                                    else
                                        wait(2)
                                    end

                                    game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'C', false, game)

                                    if MasterySkill.C.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X >= 1 or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value == false then
                                    end
                                end
                                if v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') or not v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') then
                                    repeat
                                        wait()

                                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v673.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 150, 0)
                                    until MasterySkill.C.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X <= 1 or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value == false
                                end
                                if _G.Settings.Main['Use Skill'].V == true and (MasterySkill.V.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X <= 1 and (v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (v673:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v673.Humanoid.Health > 0 and DevilFruitMastery >= MasteryDevilFruit.Lvl.V)))) then
                                    while true do
                                        if true then
                                            wait()

                                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v673.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Main['Distance Mastery'], 5)

                                            game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)

                                            if _G.Settings.Main['Hold Skill'].V ~= true then
                                                wait(0.1)
                                            else
                                                wait(2)
                                            end
                                        end

                                        game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)

                                        if MasterySkill.V.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X >= 1 or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value == false then
                                        end
                                    end
                                end
                                if v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') or not v673:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') then
                                    wait()

                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v673.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 150, 0)

                                    if MasterySkill.V.Cooldown.AbsoluteSize.X > 1 and game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild(game.Players.LocalPlayer.Data.DevilFruit.Value).Holding.Value ~= false then
                                    end
                                end
                            end
                        end
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Mastery'] and (v673.Humanoid.Health > 0 and (v673.Parent and v673.Humanoid.Health > 0)) then
                    else
                    end

                    StartMagnet = false
                    FastAttack = false

                    wait()
                    AutoHaki()
                    EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])

                    v694.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false
                    v694.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0
                    FastAttack = true

                    u171(v694.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 0))

                    if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 672))
                    end

                    sethiddenproperty(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer, 'SimulationRadius', math.huge)

                    if _G.Settings.Main['Auto KatakuriV2'] and (v694.Humanoid.Health > 0 and v694.Parent) and not (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice")) then
                    end

                    local v694

                    v679, v694 = v677(v678, v679)

                    if v679 == nil then
                    end
                    if (v694.Name == 'Diablo' or (v694.Name == 'Deandre' or v694.Name == 'Urban')) and (v694:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (v694:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and v694.Humanoid.Health > 0)) then
                    else
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)

            if p703.Name == 'Saber Expert' or (p703.Name == 'The Saw' or (p703.Name == 'Greybeard' or (p703.Name == 'Mob Leader' or (p703.Name == 'The Gorilla King' or (p703.Name == 'Bobby' or (p703.Name == 'Yeti' or (p703.Name == 'Vice Admiral' or (p703.Name == 'Warden' or (p703.Name == 'Chief Warden' or (p703.Name == 'Swan' or (p703.Name == 'Magma Admiral' or (p703.Name == 'Fishman Lord' or (p703.Name == 'Wysper' or (p703.Name == 'Thunder God' or (p703.Name == 'Cyborg' or (p703.Name == 'Don Swan' or (p703.Name == 'Diamond' or (p703.Name == 'Stone' or (p703.Name == 'Hydra Leader' or (p703.Name == 'Kilo Admiral' or (p703.Name == 'Captain Elephant' or (p703.Name == 'Beatiful Pirate' or (p703.Name == 'Cake Queen' or (p703.Name == 'rip_indra True Form' or (p703.Name == 'Longma' or (p703.Name == 'Soul Reaper' or (p703.Name == 'Cake Prince' or p703.Name == 'Dough King'))))))))))))))))))))))))))) then

                            if game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild(_G.SelectBoss) then

                        v711.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0

                        if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then

                        end

        if World3 then

            local _EliteHunter = v102.MonsterFunction:AddSection('[ Elite Hunter ]')

            EliteSpawn = _EliteHunter:AddParagraph({
                Title = '',
                Content = '',
            })

            spawn(function()
                pcall(function()
                    while wait() do
                        if game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Urban') or (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Deandre') or game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Diablo')) then
                            EliteSpawn:SetTitle('Elite NPC Status : Spawn!')
                        else
                            EliteSpawn:SetTitle('Elite NPC Status : Not Spawn!')

                        EliteSpawn:SetDesc('Elite Progress : ' .. game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('EliteHunter', 'Progress'))
                    end
                end)
            end)
            _EliteHunter:AddToggle('Elite', {
                Title = 'Auto Elite Hunter',
                Default = _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'],
            })
            _Options.Elite:OnChanged(function()
                _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'] = _Options.Elite.Value

                if _Options.Elite.Value == false then
                    wait()
                    u171(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                    wait()
                end

                SaveSettings()
            end)
            _EliteHunter:AddToggle('EliteCup', {
                Title = 'Stop Hop when got Chalice',
                Default = _G.Settings.Main['Elite Cup'],
            })
            _Options.EliteCup:OnChanged(function()
                _G.Settings.Main['Elite Cup'] = _Options.EliteCup.Value

                SaveSettings()
            end)
            _EliteHunter:AddToggle('EliteHop', {
                Title = 'Elite Hunter Hop',
                Default = _G.Settings.Main['Elite Hop'],
            })
            _Options.EliteHop:OnChanged(function()
                _G.Settings.Main['Elite Hop'] = _Options.EliteHop.Value

                SaveSettings()
            end)
            spawn(function()
                while wait() do
                    pcall(function()
                        if not _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'] then
                            if _G.Settings.Main['Elite Hop'] and _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'] then
                                if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") then
                                    if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") and _G.Settings.Main['Elite Cup'] then
                                        game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-12471.169921875, 374.94024658203, -7551.677734375))

                                        if Auto_Farm_Level then
                                            _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] = false
                                        end
                                    end
                                elseif game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('EliteHunter') == "I don't have anything for you right now. Come back later." then
                                    Hop()
                                end
                            end

                            return
                        end
                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest.Visible ~= true then
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('EliteHunter')
                        end
                        if not (string.find(game.Players.LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest.Container.QuestTitle.Title.Text, 'Diablo') or (string.find(game.Players.LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest.Container.QuestTitle.Title.Text, 'Urban') or string.find(game.Players.LocalPlayer.PlayerGui.Main.Quest.Container.QuestTitle.Title.Text, 'Deandre'))) then
                            game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('EliteHunter')
                        end

                        local v714, v715, v716 = pairs(game.ReplicatedStorage:GetChildren())

                        while true do
                            local v717

                            v716, v717 = v714(v715, v716)

                            if v716 == nil then
                                break
                            end
                            if string.find(v717.Name, 'Diablo') or (string.find(v717.Name, 'Urban') or string.find(v717.Name, 'Deandre')) then
                                if Auto_Farm_Level then
                                    _G.Settings.Main['Auto Farm Level'] = false
                                end

                                EliteHunter = u171(v717.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)

                                if (v717.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150 then
                                    if EliteHunter then
                                        EliteHunter:Stop()
                                    end

                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v717.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame
                                end
                            end
                        end

                        local v718, v719, v720 = pairs(game.Workspace.Enemies:GetChildren())
                        local v721

                        v720, v721 = v718(v719, v720)

                        if v720 == nil then
                        end
                        if not (string.find(v721.Name, 'Diablo') or (string.find(v721.Name, 'Urban') or string.find(v721.Name, 'Deandre'))) or (not v721:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') or (not v721:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') or v721.Humanoid.Health <= 0)) then
                        end
                        if true then
                            wait()
                            AutoHaki()

                            if (v721.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150 then
                                if (v721.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150 then
                                    if Farmtween then
                                        Farmtween:Stop()
                                    end

                                    game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = v721.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 30, 1)

                                    if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 672))
                                    end

                                    FastAttack = true

                                    EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                                end
                            else
                                Farmtween = u171(v721.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                            end
                        end
                        if _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'] and (v721.Parent and v721.Humanoid.Health > 0) then
                        else
                        end

                        FastAttack = false
                    end)
                end
            end)
        else
            _G.Settings.Main['Auto Elite Hunter'] = false
            _G.Settings.Main['Elite Cup'] = false
            _G.Settings.Main['Elite Hop'] = false
        end

        local _MaterialFarm = v102.ItemFunction:AddSection('[ Material Farm ]')

        _MaterialFarm:AddDropdown('MaterialSelector', {
            Title = 'Select Material to Farm',
            Values = v235,
            Multi = false,
            Default = _G.Settings.Material.Choose,
        })
        _Options.MaterialSelector:OnChanged(function()
            _G.Settings.Material.Choose = _Options.MaterialSelector.Value

            SaveSettings()
        end)
        _MaterialFarm:AddToggle('MaterialToggle', {
            Title = 'Enable Material to Get',
            Default = _G.Settings.Material.Enable,
        })
        _Options.MaterialToggle:OnChanged(function()
            _G.Settings.Material.Enable = _Options.MaterialToggle.Value

            if _Options.MaterialToggle.Value == false then
                wait()
                u171(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                wait()
            end

            spawn(function()
                while wait() and _G.Settings.Material.Enable do
                    xpcall(function()
                        if _G.Settings.Material.Choose == '' then
                            return
                        end

                        u252(_G.Settings.Material.Choose)

                        if not u241(MaterialMob) then
                            FastAttack = false
                            Modstween = u171(CFrameMon)

                            if World1 and table.find(MaterialMob, 'Fishman Commando') and (CFrameMon.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(61163.8515625, 11.6796875, 1819.7841796875))
                            elseif World1 and not table.find(MaterialMob, 'Fishman Commando') and (CFrameMon.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 50000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(3864.8515625, 6.6796875, -1926.7841796875))
                            elseif World1 and table.find(MaterialMob, "God's Guard") and (CFrameMon.Position - game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:WaitForChild('HumanoidRootPart').Position).magnitude > 3000 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                wait(0.5)
                                game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('requestEntrance', Vector3.new(-4607.8227539063, 872.54248046875, -1667.5568847656))
                            elseif (CFrameMon.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150 then
                                if Modstween then
                                    Modstween:Stop()
                                end

                                game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = CFrameMon
                            end
                        end

                        local v800, v801, v802 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:GetChildren())
                        local u803

                        v802, u803 = v800(v801, v802)

                        if v802 == nil then
                        end
                        if not _G.Settings.Material.Enable or (not table.find(MaterialMob, u803.Name) or (not u803:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') or (not u803:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') or u803.Humanoid.Health <= 0))) then
                        end

                        wait()

                        FarmtoTarget = u171(u803.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 1))

                        if u803:FindFirstChild('HumanoidRootPart') and (u803:FindFirstChild('Humanoid') and (u803.HumanoidRootPart.Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 150) then
                            if FarmtoTarget then
                                FarmtoTarget:Stop()
                            end

                            AutoHaki()

                            FastAttack = true

                            EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                            spawn(function()
                                local v804, v805, v806 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:GetChildren())

                                while true do
                                    local u807

                                    v806, u807 = v804(v805, v806)

                                    if v806 == nil then
                                        break
                                    end
                                    if u807.Name == u803.Name then
                                        spawn(function()
                                            if InMyNetWork(u807.HumanoidRootPart) then
                                                u807.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = u803.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame
                                                u807.Humanoid.JumpPower = 0
                                                u807.Humanoid.WalkSpeed = 0
                                                u807.Head.CanCollide = false

                                                if u807.Humanoid:FindFirstChild('Animator') then
                                                    u807.Humanoid.Animator:Destroy()
                                                end

                                                u807.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false

                                                u807.Humanoid:ChangeState(14)
                                                u807.Humanoid:ChangeState(11)
                                                sethiddenproperty(game.Players.LocalPlayer, 'SimulationRadius', math.huge)
                                            end
                                        end)
                                    end
                                end
                            end)

                            if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                                game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                                game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 672))
                            end
                            if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg') and game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Black Leg').Level.Value >= 150 then
                                game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(true, 'V', false, game)
                                game:service('VirtualInputManager'):SendKeyEvent(false, 'V', false, game)
                            end

                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame = u803.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, _G.Settings.Config['Distance Enemy'], 1)
                        end
                        if u241(MaterialMob) and (_G.Settings.Material.Enable and (u803.Humanoid.Health > 0 and u803.Parent)) then
                        else
                        end
                    end, function(p808)
                        print('Auto Farm Material Error : ' .. p808)
                    end)
                end
            end)
            SaveSettings()
        end)

        local _ChestFarm = v102.ItemFunction:AddSection('[ Chest Farm ]')

        _ChestFarm:AddParagraph({
            Title = 'Reminder',
            Content = 'Auto Stop Hop when got God Chalice & Fist of Darkness',
        })
        _ChestFarm:AddToggle('TweenChest', {
            Title = 'Enable Auto Tween Chest',
            Default = _G.Settings.Chest['Tween Chest'],
        })
        _Options.TweenChest:OnChanged(function()
            _G.Settings.Chest['Tween Chest'] = _Options.TweenChest.Value

            if _Options.TweenChest.Value == false then
                wait()
                u171(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                wait()
            end

            _G.MagnitudeAdd = 0

            spawn(function()
                while true do
                    if not wait() then
                        return
                    end
                    if _G.Settings.Chest['Tween Chest'] then
                        if game.ReplicatedStorage:FindFirstChild('Dough King') or (game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Dough King') or (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Darkbeard') or (game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Darkbeard') or (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Darkbeard') or (game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Darkbeard') or (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('rip_indra True Form') or (game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('rip_indra True Form') or (game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Fist of Darkness') or (game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Fist of Darkness') or (game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") or (game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild("God's Chalice") or (game.Players.LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Sweet Chalice') or game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Sweet Chalice'))))))))))))) then
                            return
                        end

                        local v810, v811, v812 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace'):GetChildren())

                        while true do
                            local v813

                            v812, v813 = v810(v811, v812)

                            if v812 == nil then
                                break
                            end

                                        end

                                        wait()

                                    end
                                end
                            end
                        end)

                        if _G.Settings.Dungeon['Select Fruit Rarity'] ~= 'Uncommon' then
                            if _G.Settings.Dungeon['Select Fruit Rarity'] == 'Rare' and (v999.Price >= 650000 and v999.Price <= 850000) then
                                table.insert(u995, v999.Name)
                            end
                        elseif v999.Price >= 250000 and v999.Price <= 600000 then
                            table.insert(u995, v999.Name)
                        end
                    elseif v999.Price >= 5000 and v999.Price <= 180000 then
                        table.insert(u995, v999.Name)
                    end
                end

                local v1000, v1001, v1002 = pairs(game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('getInventoryFruits'))

                while true do
                    local v1003

                    v1002, v1003 = v1000(v1001, v1002)

                    if v1002 == nil then
                        break
                    end

                    local v1004, v1005, v1006 = pairs(v1003)

                    while true do
                        local v1007

                        v1006, v1007 = v1004(v1005, v1006)

                        if v1006 == nil then
                            break
                        end
                        if v1006 == 'Name' then
                            table.insert(u994, v1007)
                        end
                    end
                end

                SaveSettings()
            end)

                            elseif game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1') then
                                game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').CFrame = CFrame.new(game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').CFrame.x, 60, game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').CFrame.z)

                                if (game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 350 then
                                    if (game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').Position - game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position).magnitude <= 350 then
                                        if Farmtween then
                                            Farmtween:Stop()
                                        end

                                        toTargetP(game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations['Island 1'].CFrame * CFrame.new(4, 65, 10))
                                    end
                                else
                                    Farmtween = toTargetP(game:GetService('Workspace')._WorldOrigin.Locations:FindFirstChild('Island 1').CFrame)
                                end
                            end
                        end)
                    end
                end,
            })
        end
        if World2 then
            local _LawRaid = v102.DungeonFunction:AddSection('[ Law Raid ]')

            _LawRaid:AddToggle('LawRaid', {
                Title = 'Auto Law Raid',
                Default = _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Law Raid'],
            })
            _Options.LawRaid:OnChanged(function()
                _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Law Raid'] = _Options.LawRaid.Value

                if _Options.LawRaid.Value == false then
                    wait()
                    toTargetP(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame)
                    wait()
                end

                SaveSettings()
            end)
            _LawRaid:AddButton({
                Title = 'Buy Law Chip',
                Description = 'it will Buy Law Chip | For Manual Dungeon only!',
                Callback = function()
                    game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BlackbeardReward', 'Microchip', '1')
                    game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BlackbeardReward', 'Microchip', '2')
                end,
            })
            spawn(function()
                while wait() do
                    if _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Law Raid'] then
                        pcall(function()
                            if not (game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Order') or game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Order')) then
                                if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChild('Microchip') or game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Microchip') then
                                    fireclickdetector(game:GetService('Workspace').Map.CircleIsland.RaidSummon.Button.Main.ClickDetector)
                                else
                                    game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BlackbeardReward', 'Microchip', '1')
                                    game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').Remotes.CommF_:InvokeServer('BlackbeardReward', 'Microchip', '2')
                                end
                            end
                            if not (game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Order') or game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Order')) then
                                return
                            end
                            if not game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild('Order') then
                                if game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage'):FindFirstChild('Order') then
                                    FastAttack = false

                                    toTargetP(CFrame.new(-6217.2021484375, 28.047645568848, -5053.1357421875))
                                end
                            end

                            local v1034, v1035, v1036 = pairs(game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:GetChildren())

                            while true do
                                local v1037

                                v1036, v1037 = v1034(v1035, v1036)

                                if v1036 == nil then
                                end
                                if v1037.Name == 'Order' then
                                    game:GetService('RunService').Heartbeat:wait()
                                    EquipWeapon(_G.Settings.Config['Select Weapon'])
                                    toTargetP(v1037.HumanoidRootPart.CFrame * CFrame.new(0, 50, 25))

                                    v1037.HumanoidRootPart.CanCollide = false
                                    v1037.HumanoidRootPart.Size = Vector3.new(120, 120, 120)

                                    if not _G.Settings.Config['Fast Attack'] then
                                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):CaptureController()
                                        game:GetService('VirtualUser'):Button1Down(Vector2.new(1280, 672))
                                    end

                                    FastAttack = true

                                    if v1037.Parent and (v1037.Humanoid.Health > 0 and _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Law Raid'] ~= false) and game:GetService('Workspace').Enemies:FindFirstChild(v1037.Name) then
                                    end

                                    FastAttack = false
                                end
                            end
                        end)
                    end
                end
            end)
        else
            _G.Settings.Dungeon['Auto Law Raid'] = false

            v102.DungeonFunction:AddSection('[ Law Raid ]'):AddParagraph({

        local _Ability = v102.PlayerFunction:AddSection('[ Ability ]')

        _Ability:AddButton({

            Callback = function()
                if not game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Superjump Tool') then

                    _Tool2.RequiresHandle = false
                    _Tool2.Name = 'Superjump Tool'
                    _Tool2.Parent = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack

        })
        _Ability:AddButton({
            Title = 'Fly Tool',
            Description = 'Get Tool make your Flying when you equip the tool',
            Callback = function()
                if not game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack:FindFirstChild('Fly Tool') then
                    local _Tool3 = Instance.new('Tool')
                    local _LocalPlayer5 = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer

                    _Tool3.RequiresHandle = false
                    _Tool3.Name = 'Fly Tool'
                    _Tool3.Parent = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Backpack

                    _Tool3.Equipped:Connect(function()
                        for _ = 1, 5 do
                            spawn(function()
                                local _Heartbeat = game:GetService('RunService').Heartbeat

                                Speedup = true

                                local _Character = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character
                                local v1045

                                if _Character then
                                    v1045 = _Character:FindFirstChildWhichIsA('Humanoid')
                                else
                                    v1045 = _Character
                                end

                                while Speedup and (_Heartbeat:Wait() and (_Character and (v1045 and v1045.Parent))) do
                                    if v1045.MoveDirection.Magnitude > 0 then
                                        _Character:TranslateBy(v1045.MoveDirection)
                                    end
                                end
                            end)
                        end

                        if game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character:FindFirstChildOfClass('Humanoid').RigType ~= Enum.HumanoidRigType.R6 then
                            local _UpperTorso = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.UpperTorso
                            local _BodyGyro = Instance.new('BodyGyro', _UpperTorso)

                            _BodyGyro.P = 90000
                            _BodyGyro.maxTorque = Vector3.new(9000000000, 9000000000, 9000000000)
                            _BodyGyro.cframe = _UpperTorso.CFrame

                            local _BodyVelocity4 = Instance.new('BodyVelocity', _UpperTorso)

                            _BodyVelocity4.velocity = Vector3.new(0, 0.1, 0)
                            _BodyVelocity4.maxForce = Vector3.new(9000000000, 9000000000, 9000000000)
                        else
                            local _Torso = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.Torso
                            local _BodyGyro2 = Instance.new('BodyGyro', _Torso)

                            _BodyGyro2.P = 90000
                            _BodyGyro2.maxTorque = Vector3.new(9000000000, 9000000000, 9000000000)
                            _BodyGyro2.cframe = _Torso.CFrame

                            local _BodyVelocity5 = Instance.new('BodyVelocity', _Torso)

                            _BodyVelocity5.velocity = Vector3.new(0, 0.1, 0)
                            _BodyVelocity5.maxForce = Vector3.new(9000000000, 9000000000, 9000000000)
                        end

                        local _Character2 = game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character
                        local v1053 = _Character2:FindFirstChildOfClass('Humanoid') or _Character2:FindFirstChildOfClass('AnimationController')
                        local v1054 = next
                        local v1055, v1056 = v1053:GetPlayingAnimationTracks()

                        while true do
                            local v1057

                            v1056, v1057 = v1054(v1055, v1056)

                            if v1056 == nil then
                                break
                            end

                            v1057:AdjustSpeed(0)
                        end

                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Climbing, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.FallingDown, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Flying, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Freefall, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.GettingUp, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Jumping, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Landed, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Physics, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.PlatformStanding, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Ragdoll, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Running, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.RunningNoPhysics, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Seated, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.StrafingNoPhysics, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Swimming, false)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:ChangeState(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Swimming)

                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.Humanoid.PlatformStand = true

                        while game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.Humanoid.Health == 0 do
                            game:GetService('RunService').RenderStepped:Wait()

                            if ctrl.l + ctrl.r ~= 0 or ctrl.f + ctrl.b ~= 0 then
                                speed = speed + 0.5 + speed / maxspeed

                                if speed > maxspeed then
                                    speed = maxspeed
                                end
                            elseif ctrl.l + ctrl.r == 0 and (ctrl.f + ctrl.b == 0 and speed ~= 0) then
                                speed = speed - 1

                                if speed < 0 then
                                    speed = 0
                                end
                            end
                            if ctrl.l + ctrl.r ~= 0 or ctrl.f + ctrl.b ~= 0 then
                                bv.velocity = (game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame.lookVector * (ctrl.f + ctrl.b) + (game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame * CFrame.new(ctrl.l + ctrl.r, (ctrl.f + ctrl.b) * 0.2, 0).p - game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame.p)) * speed
                                lastctrl = {
                                    f = ctrl.f,
                                    b = ctrl.b,
                                    l = ctrl.l,
                                    r = ctrl.r,
                                }
                            elseif ctrl.l + ctrl.r ~= 0 or (ctrl.f + ctrl.b ~= 0 or speed == 0) then
                                bv.velocity = Vector3.new(0, 0, 0)
                            else
                                bv.velocity = (game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame.lookVector * (lastctrl.f + lastctrl.b) + (game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame * CFrame.new(lastctrl.l + lastctrl.r, (lastctrl.f + lastctrl.b) * 0.2, 0).p - game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame.p)) * speed
                            end

                            bg.cframe = game.Workspace.CurrentCamera.CoordinateFrame * CFrame.Angles(-math.rad((ctrl.f + ctrl.b) * 50 * speed / maxspeed), 0, 0)
                        end
                    end)
                    _Tool3.Unequipped:Connect(function()
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Climbing, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.FallingDown, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Flying, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Freefall, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.GettingUp, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Jumping, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Landed, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Physics, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.PlatformStanding, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Ragdoll, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Running, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.RunningNoPhysics, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Seated, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.StrafingNoPhysics, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:SetStateEnabled(Enum.HumanoidStateType.Swimming, true)
                        _LocalPlayer5.Character.Humanoid:ChangeState(Enum.HumanoidStateType.RunningNoPhysics)

                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.UpperTorso:FindFirstChild('BodyVelocity') then
                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.UpperTorso:FindFirstChild('BodyVelocity'):Destroy()
                        end
                        if game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.UpperTorso:FindFirstChild('BodyGyro') then
                            game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.UpperTorso:FindFirstChild('BodyGyro'):Destroy()
                        end

                        Speedup = false
                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.Humanoid.PlatformStand = false
                        game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.Animate.Disabled = false
                    end)
                end
            end,
        })

                            if tostring(v1108) == '0.4' then
                                local v1109 = v1107

                                repeat
                                    wait(0.1)
                                    setupvalue(v1104, v1107, 0)
                                until not _G.Settings.Ability['Dodge No CD']

                                v1107 = v1109
                            end
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
        end)
        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                pcall(function()
                    if _G.Settings.Ability['Inf Ability'] then
                        local v1110 = game:GetService('ReplicatedStorage').FX.Agility:Clone()

                        if not game.Players.LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart:FindFirstChild('Agility') then
                            v1110.Parent = game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart
                        end
                    elseif game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Agility then
                        game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Agility:Destroy()
                    end
                end)
            end
        end)

        if game.workspace:FindFirstChild('WaterWalk') then
            game.workspace:FindFirstChild('WaterWalk'):Destroy()
        end

        platform = Instance.new('Part')
        platform.Name = 'WaterWalk'
        platform.Size = Vector3.new(15, 0.5, 15)
        platform.Anchored = true
        platform.Transparency = 1
        platform.Material = 'Neon'
        platform.Parent = game.workspace

        spawn(function()
            while wait() do
                if _G.Settings.Ability['Water Walk'] then
                    platform.CanCollide = true
                    platform.Position = Vector3.new(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.X, game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.Y * 0 - 5, game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.Z)
                else
                    platform.CanCollide = false
                    platform.Position = Vector3.new(game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.X, game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.Y * 0 - 6, game:GetService('Players').LocalPlayer.Character.HumanoidRootPart.Position.Z)
                end
            end
        end)
        v99:IgnoreThemeSettings()
        v99:SetIgnoreIndexes({})
        v100:BuildInterfaceSection(v102.Settings)
        v99:BuildConfigSection(v102.Settings)
        v101:SelectTab(1)

        local v1111 = tick()
        local v1112 = math.abs(u1 - v1111)

        u98:Notify({
            Title = 'Thunder Z Hub',
            Content = 'Successfully loaded the script in ' .. string.format('%.2f', v1112) .. 's.',
            Duration = 8,
        })
        v99:LoadAutoloadConfig()
    end

    return
end
